Note su come installare OpenBoard
---------------------------------

1) Istallare Flatpak (https://flatpak.org/setup/Ubuntu/)
  sudo apt install flatpak
  sudo apt install gnome-software-plugin-flatpak
  flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
  -restart your system
 
 2) Installa OpenBoard (https://flathub.org/apps/details/ch.openboard.OpenBoard)
 flatpak install flathub ch.openboard.OpenBoard
 
 3) run OpenBoard
    flatpak run ch.openboard.OpenBoard
